  "title": "Project Coordinator",
  "description": "<p><strong>Roles &amp; Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<p><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u>：</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Understand client requirement &amp; take charge of given tasks.</li>\n  <li>Follow-up &amp; support customers.</li>\n  <li>Collaborating with other departments to ensure sales, queries, and deliveries are handled efficiently.</li>\n  <li>Liaison between client, designer and other parties leading up to the project, ensuring client’s requirements are met and exceeded.</li>\n  <li>Prepare necessary product &amp; material base on requirements.</li>\n  <li>Support activities, manage &amp; maintain customer requirement and relationship.</li>\n  <li>Collate &amp; evaluate customer feedback and requirement of customer.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Job Requirements</strong></u>：</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>1-2 years of relevant experience preferable.</li>\n  <li>Fresh graduate is welcome.</li>\n  <li>Training will be provided.</li>\n  <li>Study in Project Manager or Interior designer welcome to join.</li>\n  <li>Able to Work independent and initiative.</li>\n  <li>Strong communication skills &amp; Self-discipline.</li>\n  <li>Active listening skills &amp; proactive communication.</li>\n  <li>Immediate available position.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Kindly provide your details in resume</strong>:</p>\n<p>- Photo</p>\n<p>- Experience &amp; Qualifications</p>\n<p>- Current &amp; Expected salaries</p>\n<p>- Date availability / Notice duration</p>",
